Hi Sarah, I’m looking for some information about your bar.

Of course! I’d be happy to help. May I start by asking for your name?

Sure, my name is John.

Great to meet you, John! Can I also have your email address so I can send you some details?

Absolutely, it’s john.doe at example dot com.

Thank you, John. One last thing, could you please provide me with your phone number for our records?

Sure, it’s six zero two- five five five- one two three four.

Thank you for that information! RT 6 Boozers is known for its great atmosphere and live music events. What specific information are you looking for?

I’d like to know about your happy hour specials.

Our happy hour runs every day from four to six PM with fifty percent off selected drinks. Thank you for your time, John! If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
